==English==
===Noun===
{{en-noun}}
#{{chemistry}} any [[organic]] [[compound]] derived from an [[oxoacid]] by replacement of a [[hydroxyl]] group by an [[aniline]] residue; an [[amide]] of aniline
#{{chemistry}} any compound in which one of the [[nitrogen]]-bound [[hydrogen]] atoms of aniline is replaced by a [[metal]] or other [[cation]]
